data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS, DEADLINE Sunday 5 pm.  OPEN HOUSE is Saturday, 4/20, 12-3pm.  Welcome to this well maintained home in the quiet Lincoln Park.  It is a lovely NO carpet, freshly painted single story, level lot, that is looking for the next homeowner!  A 3 bedroom and 2 bath, with a seperate dining, plus a breakfast bar and a nice two car garage! The chef of the home will be delighted with space and the view overlooking the backyard! Come and enjoy coffee on the covered porch!  Make your appointment today!
